author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Lola Young, who I've spoken about before, won the Rising Star Award at The Ivors last night. But it seems that not everyone is celebrating her success and she's faced claims of being an industry plant, a nepo baby and worse. Why? Isn't it time to just stop the hate?

title: Can We Stop The Hate Around Lola Young?
